text: Cornacchia is an Italian surname. Cornacchia may also refer to: * Cornacchia, a frazione of San Polo d'Enza, Reggio Emilia, Italy * Monte Cornacchia, a peak in the Monti Dauni range in southern Italy ==See also== * Cornacchia's algorithm, described in 1908 by Giuseppe Cornacchia * Stadio Adriatico – Giovanni Cornacchia, a stadium in Pescara, Abruzzo, Italy
title: Cornacchia (disambiguation)
